name: TheraPhysics Corporation
overview: Physiolink Corporation, a managed care company, designs, develops, and implements healthcare and workers’ compensation solutions for the post-acute continuum in the United States. Its solutions include custom designed panels for the coordination and management of post-acute services; and reimbursement options. The company maintains and executes the requirements of payor agreements. It serves self-funded employers, healthplans, self-funded employers, physician networks, and hospital systems. The company was formerly known as Theraphysics Corporation and changed its name to Physiolink Corporation in October 2008. The company was founded in 1991 and is based in Brentwood, Tennessee. Physiolink Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Physiotherapy Associates, Inc.
